00:20:14.159 --> 00:20:19.600
izbjegavam direktno pitanje, ali ja

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:22.280
ovako vidim zlato ide gore,

00:20:19.600 --> 00:20:25.159
nekretnine idu gore, Bitcoin ide gore,

00:20:22.280 --> 00:20:26.720
Etherium ide gore. Generalno pričamo, ne

00:20:25.159 --> 00:20:30.320
